  Version 0.4:
  * dirlisting.py: Renamed to "xmldirlisting".
  * xmldirlisting: Completely rewritten. Now outputs an XML directory listing.
  * dirlisting.css, dirlisting.js, dirlisting.xslt: Added example files for
    xml transformation with an xslt processor.

